{"id": "1514117495076814908", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "809817402287718421", "author_name": "neco9900", "author_bot": false, "content": "コラボガチャとかでしか使えない石じゃない方の石は気にせずに引きまくっていいんですか？", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T04:02:21.769000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514122321999433858", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "634053835102486558", "author_name": "asha0115", "author_bot": false, "content": "銀色の方は『しばらく引いてないなぁ』と思って気付いたら100個とか溜まってるので割とホイホイ引いちゃって大丈夫です。\nただ初期キャラのラモンナを形態変化（必須ではない）する際に60個要求されるので、変化させたくなったら控えるくらいで良いかと？", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T04:21:32.597000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514124586810343455", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1172453047708942388", "author_name": "shisu1a_kanui", "author_bot": false, "content": "ヘブンズコアは後々解放される融災禁句で4人×5チームで20人組まないといけないので引きまくって凸を進めることをおすすめします\n凸に満足したら、このゲーム限定恒常でキャラガチャの天井が共有されるので、欲しい限定の時に恒常で天井直前まで回すっていうのは考えても良いかと", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T04:30:32.570000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514126813918658580", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1222921860220452895", "author_name": "nekokin0638", "author_bot": false, "content": "質問なのですが、ヘブンズコアで25回引いてSSR覚醒体出ず、ルミナスコアで5回引いたらすり抜けがない時に限り、確定でSSR覚醒体が出るということでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T04:39:23.554000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-10T04:41:15.495000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1172453047708942388"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1514124586810343455", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514127771516014644", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1222921860220452895", "author_name": "nekokin0638", "author_bot": false, "content": "また、日替わり限定は恒常天井と共有されているのでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T04:43:11.863000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514130638456754279", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1172453047708942388", "author_name": "shisu1a_kanui", "author_bot": false, "content": "すり抜けで恒常(単PUガチャでは同界域の)SSR覚醒体、すり抜けなければ限定が出てくる、という感じ(のはず)です\n(違ったら有識者訂正お願いします)", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T04:54:35.395000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1222921860220452895"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "nanikore", "emoji_id": "1390952929443450942", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1514126813918658580", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514131473005809674", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1172453047708942388", "author_name": "shisu1a_kanui", "author_bot": false, "content": "されてます。一応キャラガチャ同士、札ガチャ同士で共有って感じなので札恒常で引いてもキャラ限定にはなんの影響もないです。\nちなみに仮天井は30、60で本天井が90です", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T04:57:54.367000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1222921860220452895"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "nanikore", "emoji_id": "1390952929443450942", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1514127771516014644", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514131822416625795", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "523378040563040256", "author_name": "long551", "author_bot": false, "content": "沙耶のために始めました\n\nステージは2章までクリア、イベントステージをキャラレンタルで少しずつやってます\n初心者がやったほうがいいこととかおすすめキャラ、編成などはありますか？\nまた、レンタルで使ったサルバドルが使いやすく、会話ログ的にも強そうなので土曜日に引くのはありですか？", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T04:59:17.673000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1514131821699272815", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-06-10-12-49-26-707_jp.co.altplus.boukyakuzenya.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 221479, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1514131821699272815/Screenshot_2026-06-10-12-49-26-707_jp.co.altplus.boukyakuzenya.jpg?ex=6a337b25&is=6a3229a5&hm=b050e2e37b9cfed4566975511855386364e9d83840d96bc361764c66c9abe525&"}, {"id": "1514131822026424382", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-06-10-12-49-07-904_jp.co.altplus.boukyakuzenya.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 232402, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1514131822026424382/Screenshot_2026-06-10-12-49-07-904_jp.co.altplus.boukyakuzenya.jpg?ex=6a337b25&is=6a3229a5&hm=0a1ecebb3e1b9f4e367037de256ee83834f0e9377e733c900ef0f6fabc533f79&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
