{"id": "1514151737009897574", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "809817402287718421", "author_name": "neco9900", "author_bot": false, "content": "おすすめルートの一部キャラ交換アイテムで代用とかもありなのかな", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T06:18:25.682000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514154970285477920", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1172453047708942388", "author_name": "shisu1a_kanui", "author_bot": false, "content": "魔封瓶なら全然可、精神カプセルとか限定にも使えるなら絶対やめた方がいい", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T06:31:16.555000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514157564789657720", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "761901376317554708", "author_name": "kura_kosame", "author_bot": false, "content": "密約というものについて教えてください。運命の札と違って誰に何が向いてるか分かりません……\nサルバドル、カーシア、ヘロット、沙耶、の編成でやっています\n深海界域を試してみたくて、いつかオレッタやトゥルーも編成に入れたいなーと思ってます", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T06:41:35.133000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-10T06:42:11.662000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514158143679238215", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1457792529335586878", "author_name": "xudabusakua", "author_bot": false, "content": "あくまで理論値みたいなものなので、多少はバラついても大丈夫だと思います。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T06:43:53.151000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514158336705167370", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1457792529335586878", "author_name": "xudabusakua", "author_bot": false, "content": "取り敢えず行けるところまで進めてみて、壁にぶち当たるようでしたらいよいよ密約を視野に入れるって流れがいいですね。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T06:44:39.172000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514159196353073182", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1457792529335586878", "author_name": "xudabusakua", "author_bot": false, "content": "今でこそ紀行札でダメ強10.8%（無凸）を誰でもつけられますけど、当時はかなり限定的で中々に盛りづらかったのです。\n個人的なおすすめとしては複合密約（3セットを2つ分装備させること）で3セット効果でダメージ強化を持つ密約を2つ分（複合）をオススメしたいですね。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T06:48:04.128000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514159646963663018", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1457792529335586878", "author_name": "xudabusakua", "author_bot": false, "content": "つまりこれとこれを合わせた密約ですね。これだけでも7.2%の火力向上が見込まれます。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T06:49:51.562000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1514159646204629083", "filename": "Screenshot_20260610-154850.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1029901, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1514159646204629083/Screenshot_20260610-154850.png?ex=6a33950f&is=6a32438f&hm=adbd79d51b2f76a62dbd556f7add8f81ed168a07eb9e971878085a174e259be9&"}, {"id": "1514159646703747182", "filename": "Screenshot_20260610-154900.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2001957, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1514159646703747182/Screenshot_20260610-154900.png?ex=6a33950f&is=6a32438f&hm=596c7b98c2ca449318554107e4aba57b79234e41891e14f3f48c2e9e5e744af0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514159836768501830", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1457792529335586878", "author_name": "xudabusakua", "author_bot": false, "content": "↑を3体分付けて、最後の1枠をラモンナ等のキーチャ要員として最後は真紅のフルセットを装備させられればなおよしです。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T06:50:36.815000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-10T06:50:59.141000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1514159836458389565", "filename": "Screenshot_20260610-154909.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1019040, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1514159836458389565/Screenshot_20260610-154909.png?ex=6a33953c&is=6a3243bc&hm=7c4c4e08cf367acfc061130df57fbe3efdd853db45cae67e6cef22430d9d9a06&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514160040171274290", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1457792529335586878", "author_name": "xudabusakua", "author_bot": false, "content": "密約解放時はこれが無難だと思います。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T06:51:25.310000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514162912279662614", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "761901376317554708", "author_name": "kura_kosame", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます！", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T07:02:50.074000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514166736524414996", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "412941973884895232", "author_name": "shibu0097", "author_bot": false, "content": "以前相談させていただいたワンダ入り狂魔パーティーで5章まで突破できました。\nお返事くれた方々ありがとうございました。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T07:18:01.845000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1514166736151253082", "filename": "Screenshot_20260609_201225.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 151697, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1514166736151253082/Screenshot_20260609_201225.jpg?ex=6a339ba9&is=6a324a29&hm=85a74c1eac7e2a2b4c7b080285d114c7ff44ea1f308098ac1d9734d3d78f6077&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514171021610188880", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "密約の種類が解放されてきたら大体これです。これ作っておけば困ることほぼ無いかなと\n【アタッカー】\n［部位］\nⅠ:率 Ⅱ:率 Ⅲ:率\nⅣ:キーチャⅤ:ダメ強 Ⅵ:ダメ強\n[転写]\nダメ強≧率>クリダメ>キーチャ\nの有機形態と墓地の囁き\n【非アタッカー】\n［部位］\nⅠ:キーチャ Ⅱ:自由 Ⅲ:ダメ強\nⅣ:キーチャⅤ:キーチャ Ⅵ:ダメ強\n[転写]\nキーチャ>ダメ強>その他\nの深紅の抱擁、無垢の黙示録、深紅3無垢3の複合", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T07:35:03.489000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["761901376317554708"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1514157564789657720", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514171617993953291", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "761901376317554708", "author_name": "kura_kosame", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます！！", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T07:37:25.678000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514172455353319517", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1169816536882626594", "author_name": "tenseikarennatomato_82997", "author_bot": false, "content": "運命の札についての質問で、恒常の札選べる輪転の書は何に使ったらいいですか？\n所持状況はこんな感じです！", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T07:40:45.320000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1514172455088951437", "filename": "IMG_4324.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1205242, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1514172455088951437/IMG_4324.png?ex=6a33a0fd&is=6a324f7d&hm=b8e53f3de0f471f51239de1330ddef651a3ccc47ba8dbc85404e3eccadd4da5e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514172646491684915", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1169816536882626594", "author_name": "tenseikarennatomato_82997", "author_bot": false, "content": "3個あります", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T07:41:30.891000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514189575361265694", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "こちら限定と恒常でガチャの天井共有されません。\nかなり分かりづらいので補足します。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T08:48:47.048000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙇‍♂️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "😭", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1514124586810343455", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514190324904235019", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "限定でも無凸で強いものは少ないですが、恒常札は3凸しないとあまり強くないものが殆どのため、同じ札を選択して凸するのが良いと思います。\nキャラの所持状況、あるいは使いたいキャラ・編成によってオススメする札が変わってきますので、宜しければお手持ちのキャラを見せていただければと思います。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T08:51:45.753000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1514172455353319517", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514192152920592435", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "523378040563040256", "author_name": "long551", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます\n5000円ぐらいとりあえず入れてみようかなとも思ってるんですが、オススメなパックとかはありますか？", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T08:59:01.586000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514196483975413870", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "ゲーム開始から60日間？限定で開放されるガチャの、「過ぎし日々の彼方」を2回引くことですかねー", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T09:16:14.190000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514197370924171334", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "課金パックでいうなら、沙耶のコラボ関係のパックで、かつイベントバナーに出ているものは大体課金効率が良いものになりますね。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T09:19:45.655000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514204023992094780", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "523378040563040256", "author_name": "long551", "author_bot": false, "content": "課金はこれだけで、プラチナジェルでコラボパック買う感じですかね？", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T09:46:11.870000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1514204023589179403", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-06-10-18-41-28-302_jp.co.altplus.boukyakuzenya.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 164664, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1514204023589179403/Screenshot_2026-06-10-18-41-28-302_jp.co.altplus.boukyakuzenya.jpg?ex=6a33be63&is=6a326ce3&hm=5a66f012d2fece6c575f758b3aba3c86f3c180d572ed642ca331dc21b05398db&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514204704027054171", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "一応、日にち単位の時間限定パックなどには直接購入のものがあります。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T09:48:54.003000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514204842673832046", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "殆どのパックは有償石購入後に有償石で購入ですね", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T09:49:27.059000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514204927126278176", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "一応注意です。おまけで付いてくる石は無償石です。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T09:49:47.194000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514205551284715613", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "過ぎし日々の彼方ガチャが終わるまでの総課金額が5000円に留まりそうであれば、5000円パック購入後に彼方ガチャ2回がオススメです。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T09:52:16.005000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1514204023992094780", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1514205708944674906", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "それ以上課金の予定があるならば、期間の短いコラボパック、特に精神体カプセルと循環基盤が報酬にあるものから購入がオススメです。", "timestamp": "2026-06-10T09:52:53.594000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
